{"title":"Peaty’s Holdfast Trail Tool Wrap Keeps Gear Close & Clean","link":"https://bikerumor.com/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-keeps-gear-close-clean/","date":1691591705000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-2.jpg\" alt=\"peaty's holdfast trail tool wrap shown on a bike\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-2.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-2-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-2-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-2-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-2-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-2-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></p>\n<p>If you’re used to strapping a tool and tube and goodness knows what else to your frame, you’re probably used to those things being muddy, dusty, and squirming around. At least that’s my experience, but the new Peaty’s Holdfast Trail Tool Wrap looks to solve all the problems with current tool wraps and straps.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1032\" height=\"1032\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-4.jpg\" alt=\"peaty's holdfast trail tool wrap hanging from a top tube\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-4.jpg 1032w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-4-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-4-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-4-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-4-768x768.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Featuring a strap plus a separate tool pouch, you put your stuff inside the pouch, which includes an internal zippered waterproof pocket for cash and other valuables, wrap it closed, then strap that to your frame.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need your stuff? The pouch can be removed without fully removing the strap from your bike, and it has a small Velcro tab so you can hang it from the strap and keep things from spilling all over the ground (or, worse, left behind).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1306\" height=\"768\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-3.jpg\" alt=\"peaty's holdfast trail tool wrap shown with various things stuffed inside it\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-3.jpg 1306w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-3-297x175.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-3-800x470.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-3-120x71.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-3-768x452.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Need a tube? Just strap it against the frame first, then separately wrap the pouch into place, letting you remove the pouch without affecting the tube’s placement. A rubberized backside keeps things from slipping and sliding, and the pouch keeps things (except the tube) clean. The pouch’s material is waterproof, so it’ll shake off a little splash, too.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"948\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-1.jpg\" alt=\"peaty's holdfast trail tool wrap\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-1.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-1-297x141.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-1-800x379.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-1-120x57.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-1-768x364.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-1-1536x728.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It comes in three colors and has reflective graphics on the exterior, perfect for adding a bit of side visibility at night. MSRP is £34.99.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://peatys.co.uk/products/holdfast-trail-tool-wrap\" target=\"_blank\">Peatys.co.uk</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/peatys-holdfast-trail-tool-wrap-keeps-gear-close-clean/\">Peaty’s Holdfast Trail Tool Wrap Keeps Gear Close &amp; Clean</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"0a027529634016373d17310ab556ee02c81c9989ec27d951f83d5cf3ad97060e","category":"Cycling"}